{"type": "article", "id": 21807, "title": "德国一个工厂房改成的儿童活动中心，看起来很友好", "description": "从外观到内在都非常实用的地方，有德国设计那种踏实的气质。", "date": "2016-02-03T15:10:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3735, "name": "德国"}, {"id": 17008, "name": "公共建筑"}, {"id": 649, "name": "儿童"}, {"id": 23089, "name": "VON M"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 158, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607173059QbPMSNYEk43ceL5v.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>小镇或乡村中的老房子被政府收回后常常用来改造成公共建筑。在德国路德维希堡(Ludwigsburg)，设计事务所 VON M 就利用工厂房来建立一个儿童和家庭活动中心（Children and Family Center ）。</p>\n<p> 现在看到的建筑有两种风格，一边是 5 幢灰色的联排公寓，另一边是白色的独立小楼。前者表面覆盖着木条，可以看到清晰的纹路和朝南的落地玻璃窗。而后者是白色的混凝土建筑，对称而简洁，开了几扇小窗。它们的纵深不同，屋顶的倾斜方向也不一致。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173050BlfTXe4AIDZr7Kkj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173050qthHWxNYoXI2Lidj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173051Swnj4iMztGbg37mZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>室内统一采用浅色的木材，房间之间相互连通，方便走动和玩耍。不同房间有着可变化调整的功能，有音乐室、阅读室、游戏室，松散地放着可移动的家具，让整体相对空旷自然。</p>\n<p>家具的主体颜色与墙面统一，一些侧面刷上了彩色，出现了明亮的变化。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173051Wx9zB3uNmYC7KZUn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173052l2xBkUsPeMNTaqpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071730522qTsz6WVAEXY93Fr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173053nmZtJfY7PHI2euca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33868809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173053Yax1ji0UV5CPJzob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33511348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173054n0l4Fc18LPTqUxiZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>一个带有小屋轮廓的椅子，是看书和午休的地方，也可以玩捉迷藏游戏。下面的四个滚轮让它可以被推到房间里的任何地方。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173054yj4L3YWSoKgCPUIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173055NIrW4CJ2sRPq1gAK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173055cQo93wOzLqjEGx02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>活动中心的设计看似简单，设计者并没有在外观上做出风格上的统一，即便是 5 幢灰色的联排公寓，屋顶的角度也不一致。他们解释称，“风格统一并一定适合儿童，我们想要提供一个友好、大方、明亮的地方，有足够的空间让他们发展自己。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173056hAXjFY4Ks3EwqDWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173056vza2NuKedH9lyoiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173057CxF7evbVLpNsH9Dm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173058oVPF5sZgR2nwEl71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607173058eR7pFiu5ktjnEqKT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/781133/children-and-family-center-in-ludwigsburg-von-m\">archdaily</a></p>\n\n\n"}